Attribution: please cite the Tumbleweed paper (FoundFold, 2026).

Provenance note: some K_D values were located through aggregator databases used only
as a PubMed-ID / citation finder. Every citation points to the original primary paper,
not the aggregator. Raw SELEX reads are not re-hosted here; see README.md for the
originating studies and accessions.
